      "content": "i'm just a bit confused... some site said the clarithromycin actually messes with how the liver processes the statin which could make the statin levels way too high in my blood. and that's dangerous. doesn't the timing not matter if they're both in my system at the same time anyway? you're saying it's fine to just keep taking them as long as i space them by a few hours?",
